Take the square plate from the counter next to the sink.
Turn around, go to the oven, and turn right to face the microwave above the oven.
Open the microwave, put the plate in the microwave, close the microwave, run the microwave for two seconds, open the microwave, take the plate from the microwave, and close the microwave.
Turn left, go to the small counter next to the refrigerator, and turn right.
Place the plate on the counter next to the refrigerator.

Place the plate down on the counter.
